UnstakeFullAmount_Integration_Concrete_Test
├── when caller not Bob
│  └── it should revert
└── when caller Bob
   ├── given Curve withdrawal requested
   │  ├── when oracle price zero
   │  │  └── it should revert
   │  └── when oracle price not zero
   │     ├── when ETH received not exceed ETH expected
   │     │  └── it should revert
   │     └── when ETH received exceeds ETH expected
   │        ├── it should unwrap wstETH to stETH
   │        ├── it should swap stETH for ETH via Curve
   │        ├── it should wrap ETH into WETH
   │        ├── it should update WETH amount received after unstaking
   │        ├── it should transfer WETH to Bob
   │        └── it should emit an {UnstakeFullAmount} event
   └── given Lido withdrawal requested
      ├── it should claim ETH from Lido withdrawal queue
      ├── it should wrap ETH into WETH
      ├── it should update WETH amount received after unstaking
      ├── it should transfer WETH to Bob
      └── it should emit an {UnstakeFullAmount} event
